{"id": "art-172", "label": "Art. 172", "title": "Art. 172: Dispunerea efectuării expertizei sau a constatării", "slug": "art-172", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1233786921\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2323\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1233786921\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 172:\nDispunerea efectu&#259;rii expertizei sau a constat&#259;rii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1676088175\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2322\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1676088175\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Efectuarea unei expertize se dispune când pentru\nconstatarea, clarificarea sau evaluarea unor fapte ori împrejur&#259;ri ce\nprezint&#259; importan&#355;&#259; pentru aflarea adev&#259;rului în cauz&#259;\neste necesar&#259; &#351;i opinia unui expert.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_387969167\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2321\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_387969167\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Expertiza se dispune, în condi&#355;iile art. 100, la\ncerere sau din oficiu, de c&#259;tre organul de urm&#259;rire penal&#259;, prin\nordonan&#355;&#259; motivat&#259;, iar în cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii se dispune\nde c&#259;tre instan&#355;&#259;, prin încheiere motivat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2035721297\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2320\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2035721297\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cererea de efectuare a expertizei trebuie formulat&#259;\nîn scris, cu indicarea faptelor &#351;i împrejur&#259;rilor supuse\nevalu&#259;rii &#351;i a obiectivelor care trebuie l&#259;murite de expert.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1070687767\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2319\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1070687767\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Expertiza poate fi efectuat&#259; de exper&#355;i\noficiali din laboratoare sau institu&#355;ii de specialitate ori de\nexper&#355;i independen&#355;i autoriza&#355;i din &#355;ar&#259; sau din\nstr&#259;in&#259;tate, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_988146691\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2318\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_988146691\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Expertiza &#351;i examinarea medico-legal&#259; se\nefectueaz&#259; în cadrul institu&#355;iilor medico-legale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_338559653\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2317\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_338559653\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Ordonan&#355;a organului de urm&#259;rire penal&#259;\nsau încheierea instan&#355;ei prin care se dispune efectuarea expertizei\ntrebuie s&#259; indice faptele sau împrejur&#259;rile pe care expertul trebuie\ns&#259; le constate, s&#259; le clarifice &#351;i s&#259; le evalueze,\nobiectivele la care trebuie s&#259; r&#259;spund&#259;, termenul în care\ntrebuie efectuat&#259; expertiza, precum &#351;i institu&#355;ia ori\nexper&#355;ii desemna&#355;i.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1422737862\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2316\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1422737862\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)În domeniile strict specializate, dac&#259; pentru\nîn&#355;elegerea probelor sunt necesare anumite cuno&#351;tin&#355;e specifice\nsau alte asemenea cuno&#351;tin&#355;e, instan&#355;a ori organul de\nurm&#259;rire penal&#259; poate solicita opinia unor speciali&#351;ti care\nfunc&#355;ioneaz&#259; în cadrul organelor judiciare sau în afara acestora.\nDispozi&#355;iile relative la audierea martorului sunt aplicabile în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_444354035\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2315\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_444354035\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)La efectuarea expertizei pot participa exper&#355;i\nindependen&#355;i autoriza&#355;i, numi&#355;i la solicitarea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor sau subiec&#355;ilor procesuali principali.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_911079709\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2314\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_911079709\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Când exist&#259; pericol de dispari&#355;ie a unor\nmijloace de prob&#259; sau de schimbare a unor situa&#355;ii de fapt ori este\nnecesar&#259; l&#259;murirea urgent&#259; a unor fapte sau împrejur&#259;ri ale\ncauzei, organul de urm&#259;rire penal&#259; poate dispune prin\nordonan&#355;&#259; efectuarea unei constat&#259;ri.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_79561929\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2313\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_79561929\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Constatarea este efectuat&#259; de c&#259;tre un\nspecialist care func&#355;ioneaz&#259; în cadrul organelor judiciare sau din\nafara acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_27687329\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2312\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_27687329\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Certificatul medico-legal are valoarea unui raport de\nconstatare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_114561719\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2311\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_114561719\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)Dup&#259; finalizarea raportului de constatare, când\norganul judiciar apreciaz&#259; c&#259; este necesar&#259; opinia unui expert\nsau când concluziile raportului de constatare sunt contestate, se poate dispune\nefectuarea unei expertize.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}